=== Overview

template-simple is used as a template for new simple mixins group creation.

==== Options

--- true
This option will enable simple group creation template and show mixins parameter basic usage.

    --- parameters
        - para1: "mixins parameter example"
        - para2: "mixins parameter example"

    --- code dir
        - N/A
        - N/A

    --- deps
        - N/A


--- false
This option will disable simple group creation template.


--- default
when not explicitly selected in mixin spec file, the default option will be used.
